node.text:
The kid from the hood who knew he could.. ⁣
⁣
2020 has been the biggest blessing in my life,⁣
I’m glad that I am in the position I am in now.⁣
⁣
To be able to be the person that is looked up to in my community and set the standard for my friends and family is an incredible feeling.
⁣
I hope everybody continues to push through such odd times in our world and works to add value and uplift others. Absolutely crush the rest of the month and prepare for the sprint that will be next year. ⁣
⁣
2020 was just the beginning,⁣
⁣
2021 is not ready for Kid Kash.

node.text:
If your dream ain’t bigger than you,⁣⁣⁣⁣
There’s a problem with your dream 💯⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
@deionsanders spoke these words and there’s not a better message I believe that I could give you guys on this Friday. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
This man truly is an inspiration. Being a defensive back that has a similar style of play he’s always been the guy I emulated on the field & as I grew I realized that he’s a true role model off the field & that’s the legacy I want to leave.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
People will try to shoot down your dreams because they’re too big, the real reason they discredit you is because they’re scared you’ll actually make it. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
After my second heart surgery, I had friends & family tell me I should never step foot on a football field again. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
How could all these people try to tell me not to do what I love? What’s given me the life I live?⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
I thought they loved me...⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
I realized it’s just that these same people didn’t want to see me make it because they know I would! Now everyday I wake up I see my vision and get after it. I know what it takes. Like @deionsanders always says: “You look good, you feel good. You feel good, you play good. You play good, they pay good.” ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Wake up & be passionate, dream big, get after it. We only get to live this life one time. Live it how you want to live it, with no regrets! It’s a blessing after all.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
𝐏𝐞𝐚𝐜𝐞 & 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞. 𝐄𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲𝐛𝐨𝐝𝐲 𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐧 𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐳𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐰𝐞𝐞𝐤𝐞𝐧𝐝! 𝐇𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐬𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐟𝐮𝐧, 𝐛𝐞 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐝, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐲 𝐬𝐚𝐟𝐞 𝐚𝐬 𝐚𝐥𝐰𝐚𝐲𝐬! 💕💕
